On Escalation Ticket # 00423829 the new comment has been added: Jonathan Micheal Orford:

@WaitingOnEngineer 
/etc/nginx/nginx.conf was incorrectly configured as such:


access_log off;
error_log off;


Should be:


access_log off;
error_log /dev/null;


OR



access_log off;
error_log /var/log/nginx/error.log crit;


This setting has never changed. 


The monitoring and escalation flow from the automated AWS DevOps monitoring to technical support ticketing is not working. This is being discussed between Paul and Bogdan.


Jono

